ReplaceBNbyTerms-sh :


1-GenerateBNTermsList-horizontal.sh :
Generate a list of references from a matrix whose bn:ID and terms are in the
first line (header).

1-GenerateBNTermsList-vertical.sh :
Generate a list of references from a matrix whose bn:ID and terms are in the
first column.


2-ReplaceTermsBNbyBN.sh :
Replace the "Term bn:ID" by the bn:ID only

2-ReplaceTermsBNbyTerms.sh :
Replace the "Term bn:ID" by the term only


3-ReplaceBNbyTerms.sh :
Replace the bn:ID by the word equivalent in every document.
(uses a reference file from 1-GenerateBNTermsList-*.sh)
